mechs: *Despair Effects:*  whenever butch sings more the more despair you become, which makes your screen more dark & the more health drain you get.
bio:
On a foggy night, you've found the old butch you've always hated, expect he looks more different, starving to eat anyone he see.
you have the determination to stop that monster, but he won't make it easy for goaling to leaving you in despair before dying...
